Fried chicken is a globally loved food, and can be found in almost every restaurant locally and internationally.  Today marks National Fried Chicken Day, and this day was put in place to recognise and celebrate the delicious fried chicken.  Enjoy fried chicken with a twist today by recreating these delicious and flavourful southern fried chicken tacos in celebration of National Fried Chicken Day.   ALSO TRY: Recipe of the day: Homemade chicken pad Thai This recipe was found on sweetcsdesigns.com